{"tid":711026,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"哥倫比亞球迷教日本球迷講西班牙話引發外交風波","createTime":"2018-06-21T08:25:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-21T12:17:54.000Z","uid":55981,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"b1516ae2b5a0ad1d1ca9bc616b07689b8c8a739c","tid":711026,"uid":55981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T08:25:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://livedoor.blogimg.jp/sekaiminzoku/imgs/9/8/982142b6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Flivedoor.blogimg.jp%2Fsekaiminzoku%2Fimgs%2F9%2F8%2F982142b6.jpg&h=253a792c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/Rmiraflorestv/status/1009239801072095232\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FRmiraflorestv%2Fstatus%2F1009239801072095232&d=TIjPz5sjqPVI6l%2FEJ%2BrCdJUWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=832d4c57\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FRmiraflorestv%2Fstatus%2F1009239801072095232&h=1b029859\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/Rmiraflorestv/status/1009239801072095232</a><br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯世界盃決賽周，日前舉行 H 組首輪比賽，日本對哥倫比亞；日本以 2：1「爆冷」勝出。賽後日本球迷「自己垃圾自己拾」，自己帶垃圾袋在球場清理自己製造的垃圾，據稱哥倫比亞球迷都有幫手兼恭賀日本旗開得勝。以為日軍與哥倫比亞就此一團和氣你就輸了。「開賽幾分鐘送張紅牌我嘆」，條氣一定唔肯順，所以&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n所謂十隻手指有長短，哥倫比亞球迷也不是全部友善的。據悉在比賽當天結束後，就有壞份子「滋事」。一名哥倫比亞男球迷，教兩位俏麗妙齡日本女球迷講西班牙文，講的卻是：「我係母狗、我係妓女」！事件更被拍成短片，在網絡瘋傳。因為輸波想出氣？抑或天生衰格？無論如何，都係冇品！<br />\n<br />\n「我係妓女」短片被瘋傳，就連哥倫比亞足球名宿 Faustino Asprilla 艾斯派拿，都在個人 Twitter 發帖轉載短片，並向日本人公開道歉。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2095000/2098900/20180620_colum_03_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2095000%2F2098900%2F20180620_colum_03_600.jpg&h=3b99e435&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n哥倫比亞外交部譴責事件<br />\n<br />\n哥倫比亞外交部 twitter 亦發帖譴責：「該哥倫比亞男球迷的行為非但不尊重女性，更有侮辱哥國與其他國家文化之嫌；我們歡迎球迷穿起哥倫比亞球衣，在世界盃宣揚彼此尊重，反對侮辱行為，該等行為不代表我們的文化、語言或種族。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2095000/2098900/20180620_colum_04_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2095000%2F2098900%2F20180620_colum_04_600.jpg&h=4f010dba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2098900\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2098900&d=TIjPz5sjqPVI6l%2FEJ%2BrCdJUWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=53fc27b6\" target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2098900</a>"},{"pid":"efd6a276e8ef0290683d43b4daa7dacde0ee36f7","tid":711026,"uid":61327,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T08:27:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d7065e7e7bf0039ddf003dba6ec000e681e89a4","tid":711026,"uid":19126,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T08:28:25.000Z","msg":"哥倫比亞都有連登仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/goal.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5c7956b4b73143638f7fe959ad7b74292b8afb0","tid":711026,"uid":54373,"like":29,"dislike":1,"score":28,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T09:04:13.000Z","msg":"教兩位俏麗妙齡日本女球迷講西班牙文，講的卻是：「麻友係母狗、麻友係妓女」"},{"pid":"39bb1950ac3927a1d6fc92345df27faafdd8c55b","tid":711026,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T09:07:26.000Z","msg":"MAYU IS G"},{"pid":"f2126ac3cd68b984e08e852544e6f93f234f8db0","tid":711026,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T09:11:48.000Z","msg":"麻友係雞"},{"pid":"062404032b9f70d24719cf22a0015db193